# Environment Variables Template

## Frontend (.env)
```env
# API Configuration
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api/v1
REACT_APP_ENV=development

# App Info
REACT_APP_APP_NAME=Smart WMS
REACT_APP_VERSION=1.0.0

# Features
REACT_APP_ENABLE_NOTIFICATIONS=true
REACT_APP_ENABLE_AUTO_REFRESH=true
REACT_APP_AUTO_REFRESH_INTERVAL=30000

# Theme
REACT_APP_PRIMARY_COLOR=#0284c7
REACT_APP_THEME=light
```

## Backend (.env)
```env
# Server
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development

# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://wms_user:secure_password_123@localhost:5432/smart_wms

# Cache
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# Services
AI_ENGINE_URL=http://localhost:8001

# Authentication
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-key-change-in-production
JWT_EXPIRY=24h

# Logging
LOG_LEVEL=debug

# CORS
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000

# Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT=100
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW=60000
```

## AI Engine (.env)
```env
# Server
PORT=8001
WORKERS=4
LOG_LEVEL=INFO

# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://wms_user:secure_password_123@localhost:5432/smart_wms

# Cache
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# Models
MODEL_PATH=./models
MODEL_VERSION=v1_2024_02_21

# ML Config
BATCH_SIZE=32
EPOCHS=100
LEARNING_RATE=0.001

# Training Schedule
TRAINING_DAY=0  # 0 = Sunday
TRAINING_TIME=02:00  # 2:00 AM
TRAINING_ENABLED=true

# Inference
INFERENCE_TIMEOUT=100  # milliseconds
CACHE_TTL=3600  # 1 hour

# Monitoring
ENABLE_METRICS=true
METRICS_PORT=9090
```

## Production Database (.env)
```env
# PostgreSQL Production
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://prod_user:CHANGE_ME@prod-db.azure.com:5432/smart_wms_prod
DATABASE_POOL_SIZE=20
DATABASE_SSL=true

# Redis Production
REDIS_URL=redis://prod-redis.azure.com:6379?ssl=true

# AI Engine Production
AI_ENGINE_URL=https://ai-engine.azureapps.net/api/v1

# Security
JWT_SECRET=USE_STRONG_RANDOM_KEY_HERE
ENABLE_HTTPS=true
SSL_CERT_PATH=/etc/ssl/certs/server.crt
SSL_KEY_PATH=/etc/ssl/private/server.key

# Monitoring
LOG_LEVEL=info
SENTRY_DSN=https://xxxxx@sentry.io/xxxxx
NEW_RELIC_LICENSE_KEY=xxxxx
```

